(3322, 219, 'days_1_day_additional_desc', '<ul>\r\n 	<li>Breakfast: 8:30-10:00 AM\r\n<h3>Location: Singer Palace Hotel</h3>\r\n<h4>At the “Rooftop”</h4>\r\n*Reservation is required\r\n*Leaving from hotel to location at: 8:15 AM\r\nWalking distance: 13 minuets\r\nBy car: 7 minutes\r\n<a href=\"https://www.singerpalacehotel.com/en/rooftop-restaurant/\">https://www.singerpalacehotel.com/en/rooftop-restaurant/</a></li>\r\n 	<li>Open bus tour: Your tour will start between: 10:15-10:30 AM</li>\r\n 	<li>Duration: 1 hour,40 minuets\r\nYour tour will end up at: noon\r\nPick up location: several\r\nOperator: BigBus Tours,Purple RouteValidation: 2 days\r\nPrice: 35€/person=150 SAR</li>\r\n 	<li>Fatamorgana Gelato+Trevi FountainEnjoy your gelato!\r\n\r\n12:30-1:30 PM</li>\r\n 	<li>Galleria alberto sordi shopping arcade &amp; lunch at “Antico Cafe Greco”\r\nWalking distance: 8 minuets “from galleria to caffe”\r\n02:00-04:00 PM</li>\r\n 	<li>You may get back to hotel to rest</li>\r\n 	<li>Vespa or ape calessino night tour &amp; pizza</li>\r\n 	<li>Tour starting at: 07:30 PM\r\n\r\nDuration: 3 hours\r\n\r\nType: vespa with driver\r\n\r\nRate per 3: 435€=1900 SAR</li>\r\n</ul>'),
